<section id="cta">
  <div class="dashboard-panel final reveal">
    <div class="label-mono lime eyebrow">05 â Prochaine ÃĐtape</div>
    <h2>PrÃŠt Ã  te lancer ?</h2>
    <p class="copy">
      La cohorte 1 dÃĐmarre <strong>mi-mai 2026</strong>. 7 places.<br />
      Le prix le plus bas qu'il y aura jamais. Si tu hÃĐsites, rÃĐserve un call â on en parle 15 minutes et tu dÃĐcides aprÃĻs.
    </p>
    <div class="ctas">
      <a href="https://cal.com/lilian-sevoumian/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary" data-fast-goal="click_cta_primaire_last">
        SÃĐcuriser ma place <span class="arr" aria-hidden="true">â</span>
      </a>

      <form id="waitlist-form" class="waitlist-form" novalidate>
        <label for="waitlist-email" class="sr-only">Email pour la liste d'attente</label>
        <input
          id="waitlist-email"
          name="email"
          type="email"
          required
          autocomplete="email"
          placeholder="ton@email.com"
          class="waitlist-input"
        />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary waitlist-submit" data-fast-goal="click_cta_secondaire">
          Rejoindre la liste d'attente
        </button>
        <p id="waitlist-status" class="waitlist-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
